te><blockquote>遲 D 話 iPhone 都跟出 Edge .. 係就痴撚線.<br />\n<br />\nEdge 係史上最撚廢既設計, 我影過相兩邊兩條反光能量棒. 重有影像變形?  當年廢寶買左無耐就放你就知幾垃圾.</blockquote><br />\n設計既野你撚識咩<br />\n咁講2.5d 玻璃夠無用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6132679&amp;page=3&amp;highlight_id=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6132679%26page%3D3%26highlight_id%3D0&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a7b1ec15\" target=\"_blank\">http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6132679&amp;page=3&amp;highlight_id=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://a66.tinypic.com/3305xtk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa66.tinypic.com%2F3305xtk.jpg&h=daf81572&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有 Edge 望清楚兩邊係變左藍同埋 D 左邊 icon 有 d 變型 <br />\n右上角個 PM 慘不忍睹 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://a68.tinypic.com/2mgjzg7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa68.tinypic.com%2F2mgjzg7.jpg&h=8c1cfb02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有 Edge 係瀏覽器左右有兩條藍光, 左右 keyboard 歪左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://a65.tinypic.com/2h2ipa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa65.tinypic.com%2F2h2ipa0.jpg&h=c83902d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無 Edge 有 keyboard 係瀏覽器正正常常 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://a65.tinypic.com/2dhtu6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa65.tinypic.com%2F2dhtu6d.jpg&h=c0db9a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有 Edge SMS 左右藍光又再出現, More 又歪左, send 制又好似溶左吸左落一邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://a67.tinypic.com/2bumqg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa67.tinypic.com%2F2bumqg.jpg&h=86bac13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無 Edge SMS 正正常常, 係 AMOLED 既刺眼 <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> 如果話兩邊藍光係唔影響, 左右兩邊顯示變歪係唔影響閱讀, 我話好野就係咁解.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個 Edge 就係一個為出而出既失敗作, 每個買家比錢三叔讀書. <br />\n人地 LG 有兩個 mon 就真係做到有用功能. <br />\n三星呢 D 敗類根本就害緊 Android, 又佢出 Bada 同 Touchwiz 就知. 再加上 samsung store, samsung pay, s voice .. 支持 Android 就應該推低三叔. <br />\n<br />\n係呀, 我真係放工落去試機. 唔係一個打手係電腦面前勁?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=lC1pBoxvpzw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlC1pBoxvpzw&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9ae0b8a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=lC1pBoxvpzw</a><br />\n無心機睇晒就條去 1:40 睇下條邊變左白邊  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇片部機重撚戇鳩上下無撚左忽比個圈位食撚埋  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.02 分講撚埋個 edge 會有 D distract, 個 band 會有影響成型.<br />\n3.13 分講既 sidebar 跟條反光白邊. 成盤根本就係失敗作品  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係囉 youtube 條片又係 ifan, 總知唔撚合你意就係 ifan 囉 </blockquote>"},{"pid":"96e622188bd4a5cf53d49c9a25b35c9a2a7299fe","tid":188053,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"得個靚字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38858b1c2c8b2bc74a11a730439351ed3f175198","tid":188053,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6e0f4f6cd4496a2d2924d3176a35086fa3ec4b","tid":188053,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:17:43.000Z","msg":"2.5D 玻璃同 3D 根本係兩樣野.  您越講就只會越顯得用 3D 為出而出既低智.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.androidauthority.com/twitter-lite-data-friendly-mobile-web-app-thats-optimized-speed-762025/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidauthority.com%2Ftwitter-lite-data-friendly-mobile-web-app-thats-optimized-speed-762025%2F&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=4e9aea